      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely obsessed with this car, but it's finally time for it to find a new lucky owner. Honestly, it is in such stunning condition\u2014it feels just like stepping onto the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it sparkling clean and pampered since day one. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for your next big adventure, this is definitely the one. I'd love to tell you more about it, so don't be shy\u2014reach out and let's chat!",
