    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing to achieve a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission delivers power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics with zero bushing deflection or fluid seepage. A true purist\u2019s specimen with no cosmetic or mechanical compromises.",
