    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute dream of a car. It\u2019s in seriously incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. You really have to see it to believe how clean it is\u2014come take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
